    "Id": "chassisdef_katana_CRK-5003-2OS",
    "Name": "Katana",
    "Details": "The CRK-5003-2OS is the personal BattleMech of Warlord Oruko Saki. It has a configuration very close to the standard CRK-5003-2 with only a few upgrades. The 'Mech's primary weapons systems remain the same: two Large Lasers backed up by a single LB 10-X Autocannon. The 'Mech also retains the two standard Short Range Missile racks. A secondary system of small lasers rounds out the 'Mech's offensive powers, mounted one in each arm and one in the rear torso. One of the few upgrades to Saki's Katana comes in the form of C.A.S.E. installed into the 'Mech's right torso. The other upgrade comes in the form of fifteen high-efficiency heat sinks replacing the CRK-5003-2's normal twenty heat sinks.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Easy to Pilot</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.2</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Lower, Right Lower</color>",
